effect was captured by the FACIT-F and FACT-Th6 among patients who experienced 
sustained platelet responses.
CONCLUSIONS: Results provide support for the validity, reliability, and 
responsiveness of the FACIT-F, FACT-Th6, and SF-36v2 in chronic ITP patients.

